column1: Declension of college (irregular)  singular  plural  nominative  /ˈko̞lidsi/ or /ˈko̞lids/  /ˈko̞lidsit̪/  genitive  /ˈko̞lidsin/  /ˈko̞lidsie̞n/  partitive  /ˈko̞lidsiɑ/  /ˈko̞lidse̞jɑ/  accusative  /ˈko̞lidsi/ or /ˈko̞lids//ˈko̞lidsin/  /ˈko̞lidsit̪/  inessive  /ˈko̞lidsisːɑ/  /ˈko̞lidse̞isːɑ/  elative  /ˈko̞lidsistɑ/  /ˈko̞lidse̞istɑ/  illative  /ˈko̞lidsiːn/  /ˈko̞lidse̞iɦin/  adessive  /ˈko̞lidsilːɑ/  /ˈko̞lidse̞ilːɑ/  ablative  /ˈko̞lidsiltɑ/  /ˈko̞lidse̞ilt̪ɑ/  allative  /ˈko̞lidsilːe̞/  /ˈko̞lidse̞ilːe̞/  essive  /ˈko̞lidsinɑ/  /ˈko̞lidse̞inɑ/  translative  /ˈko̞lidsiksi/  /ˈko̞lidse̞iksi/  instructive  –  /ˈko̞lidse̞in/  abessive  /ˈko̞lidsit̪ːɑ/  /ˈko̞lidse̞it̪ːɑ/  comitative  –  /ˈko̞lidse̞ine̞ːn/
